data.description: 2 acre beauty in the Award Winning McIntosh school district. Drive up the tree lined driveway to this charming brick front colonial.  A formal living and dining room flank the elegant two story foyer.  Den area &  family room both  contain fabulous  gas starter fireplace. Covered porch leading to the driveway &  2 Car garage w  finished bonus area & Separate entrance off backyard.  The second story holds 4 bedrooms and a bonus room w closet . The oversized master bedroom  overlooks your 2 acre backyard. The master bath has an oversized stand alone shower and restful soaking tub. Finished basement.  Private & gated Salt water pool w tranquil waterfall,  Koi Pond, fire pit, Beautiful pavers, Pergola over deck. Take a peaceful stroll on the property's trails surrounded by secluded woods. Playhouse and playground convey w home.NO need to go on vacation, you've arrived!  All new lightning fixtures  & Home is Freshly painted.   Easy connect to Peachtree City golf cart paths only .4 mile!!  Inground Sprinkler system,  Call listing agent with any questions 678-770-5269
